Afficher les différence trouvée dans le log.
forever continu si erreur !



BEWARE : the regression tests are quite special.
They didnt' tell if the application is working, they tell if
the application give the same result than the last time.

In order to use these regression tests :
   * You checkout a working version
   * You run the regression tests
   * You checkout the next version
   * You run the regression tests

If there is GUI change, the tests will fail.





======================
Testing IE from Linux.
======================

---------
ies4linux
---------

'ies4linux' works nicely until some DNS errors: unusable

---------
    VNC
---------
* Install 'tightvnc' under vista home
* Allow port '3389' on windows firewall
* Run 'tightvnc' server
* Set tight vnc server :
	- Correct port
	- Set password ''
	- Allow empty password
	- Run IE
	- Set the window to display to be IE one
	- Close preference (does not work if you don't)
	- Activate the IE window to put it in focus
* On linux install 'xtightvncviewer'
* To run the IE window :

  xtightvncviewer 192.168.0.131::3389 -encodings raw -compresslevel 1 -nojpeg \
                  -x11cursor